179	    /// <summary>True when <paramref name="dir"/> holds at least one non-ignored, non-README <c>*.md</c>
180	    /// directly or in a direct subdirectory — the same one-level-deep window the ADR enumeration reads, so a
181	    /// probe never resolves to a directory generation would then find empty. Bounded on purpose (never a
182	    /// whole-tree walk). README is excluded from the content check (though it still renders as the ADR
183	    /// landing page if the candidate is chosen) so a folder holding only landing-page prose doesn't win the
